data.description: Stunning newer home nestled on a spacious 1-acre lot with easy access to Boise. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features a formal dining area and ample room for a shop. Enjoy an open floor plan showcasing premium upgrades. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, a large island, soft-close drawers and cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Engineered hardwood flooring flows throughout, complemented by a striking tile fireplace in the great room. A convenient walk-in pantry and laundry room adjoin the kitchen.  Notable features include LED lighting and elegant rope lighting in the great room ceiling. The master suite offers a generous walk-in closet, double sinks, and exquisite quartz finishes in the floor-to-ceiling tiled shower. Outside, relax on the inviting covered patio. This home combines luxury and functionality in a desirable location.
